{
  "stem": "15393.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then I heard, not on one occasion, look at her, look at that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "If she weren't German, you'd-- you would know she is a Jew.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Only because I was dark.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I heard that not on one occasion.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was petrifying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was also frightened that somebody may recognize me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They might have known me from before, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's-- it's-- it was all very possible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I did this terribly unpleasant and not nice thing by going straight to the front and demanding to be served.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's the way we got some food up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On one such occasion, I was-- there was a very small queue, and they were mostly German women.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "About three people in front, so I didn't want to do my bit that way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I queued, stood there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was nearly my turn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I produced my thing, because my money was in it, and went to take the money out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And suddenly, from behind me, I hear, oh, dear God, this is [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sepi. ?] And a man embracing me from the back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and I froze, absolutely froze.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had no idea who I'm dealing with, what it is.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this is [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sepi ?] was-- was bad, was very bad news.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the man sort of let's go and looks at me this way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and says, where is he?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Where is your papi?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Where is he?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I immediately realized, this must be somebody who knows him very well, because I didn't keep that for such a long time, just literally took the money out.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And where is your papi?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I mean-- Oh, I said, my papi, my papi is on the Eastern Front.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He's not here at all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was in a terrible schtuck.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
